Company Profile

						Siam Pan Group Public Co.,Ltd (SPG), registration no. Bor Mor Jor 612, with head office located at 488
						Nakornsawan Rosd, Kwang Siyak-Mahanak, Dusit, Bangkok, Tel 02-2800202-17 Fax 02-2806305 and its warehouse
						located at 60 Moo 3, Soi Jai-ua, Tambol Bangkayang, Ampur Muang, Patumthani. The company's registered and
						paid up capital is Baht 345.00 million. The company is the distributor of lubricating oils, greases, and
						automotive batteries manufactured by its 3 subsidiaries, whose details of business are as follows: 
					



